  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multimodal analgesia may be important for optimal postoperative pain treatment and
      facilitation of early mobilization and recovery. This study investigated the analgesic effect
      of pregabalin and dexamethasone in patients undergoing lumbar spinal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
